{"tha-ap321:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap321:0.2":"Arakkhadayakavagga ","tha-ap321:0.3":"9 Kandalipupphiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap321:1.1":"“Sindhuya nadiya tire, ","tha-ap321:1.2":"ahosim kassako tada; ","tha-ap321:1.3":"Parakammayane yutto, ","tha-ap321:1.4":"parabhattam apassito. ","tha-ap321:2.1":"Sindhum anucarantoham, ","tha-ap321:2.2":"siddhattham jinamaddasam; ","tha-ap321:2.3":"Samadhina nisinnamva, ","tha-ap321:2.4":"satapattamva pupphitam. ","tha-ap321:3.1":"Satta kandalipupphani, ","tha-ap321:3.2":"vante chetvanaham tada; ","tha-ap321:3.3":"Matthake abhiropesim, ","tha-ap321:3.4":"buddhassadiccabandhuno. ","tha-ap321:4.1":"Suvannavannam sambuddham, ","tha-ap321:4.2":"Anukule samahitam; ","tha-ap321:4.3":"Tidhapabhinnamatangam, ","tha-ap321:4.4":"Kunjaramva durasadam. ","tha-ap321:5.1":"Tamaham upagantvana, ","tha-ap321:5.2":"nipakam bhavitindriyam; ","tha-ap321:5.3":"Anjalim paggahetvana, ","tha-ap321:5.4":"avandim satthuno aham. ","tha-ap321:6.1":"Catunnavutito kappe, ","tha-ap321:6.2":"yam pupphamabhiropayim; ","tha-ap321:6.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap321:6.4":"buddhapujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap321:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap321:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap321:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap321:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kandalipupphiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap321:9.1":"Kandalipupphiyattherassapadanam navamam. "}